Titolo: Mickey Mousecapade

Anno: 1987

Descrizione: Mickey Mousecapade, released in Japan as Mickey Mouse: Fushigi no Kuni no Daibouken (ミッキーマウス 不思議の国の大冒険, "Mickey Mouse: Adventures in Wonderland"), is a platform game developed by Hudson Soft and published by Capcom originally in 1987 for the Family Computer (Famicom) in Japan. Capcom released the game for the Nintendo Entertainment System (NES) in the United States. 
The character of Mickey Mouse attempts to save a young girl who happens to be Alice from Alice in Wonderland. Minnie Mouse follows Mickey around and occasionally gets kidnapped. Various villains from Disney cartoons and animated films make an appearance as bosses.